# Environment Variables Required

## Stripe Configuration

### Backend (Server Actions)
```
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_xxxxx
```

### Frontend (Client Components)
```
NEXT_PUBLIC_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_xxxxx
```

## Supabase Configuration
```
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your-service-role-key
```

## Ansonia (Equifax) Credit API Integration
```
ANSONIA_API_URL=https://api.ansoniadata.com/v1
ANSONIA_API_KEY=your-ansonia-api-key
ANSONIA_ACCOUNT_ID=your-ansonia-account-id
```

## Airtable Integration for Manual Review Queue (DEPRECATED)
```
AIRTABLE_API_KEY=your-airtable-api-key
AIRTABLE_BASE_ID=your-airtable-base-id
AIRTABLE_TABLE_NAME=Manual Review Queue
```

## Salesforce Integration (NEW - Single Source of Truth)
```
# OAuth2 Configuration
SALESFORCE_CLIENT_ID=your-connected-app-client-id
SALESFORCE_CLIENT_SECRET=your-connected-app-secret
SALESFORCE_REDIRECT_URI=http://localhost:3000/api/auth/salesforce/callback

# Direct API Authentication
SALESFORCE_INSTANCE_URL=https://your-instance.salesforce.com
SALESFORCE_USERNAME=your-integration-user@hitchyard.com
SALESFORCE_PASSWORD=your-integration-password
SALESFORCE_SECURITY_TOKEN=your-security-token
SALESFORCE_ACCESS_TOKEN=your-refresh-or-access-token

# Dify Integration
DIFY_API_KEY=your-dify-api-key
DIFY_BASE_URL=https://your-dify-instance.com/api
```

## Site Configuration
```
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=http://localhost:3000
# For production: https://yourdomain.com
```

## How to Set Up

1. Create a `.env.local` file in the project root
2. Copy the variables above and fill in your actual values
3. Get Stripe keys from: https://dashboard.stripe.com/test/apikeys
4. Get Supabase values from your Supabase project settings

## Important Notes

- Use `sk_test_` and `pk_test_` for development
- Use `sk_live_` and `pk_live_` for production
- Never commit `.env.local` to version control (it's in .gitignore)
- Vercel/deployment platforms have their own environment variable settings
